data.description: Single level craftsman style home nestled amongst the trees and park like setting of Oregon Water Wonderland. This 3 bedroom 2 bath charmer has everything you have been looking for and more. The renovated kitchen is the heart of the home and invites you to entertain and create wonderful memories. Relax on the front deck while admiring the beautiful landscaping. Invite family and friends over for a BBQ on the spacious back patio while enjoying the serenity of the fully fenced backyard. Just shy of a half-acre, there's plenty of room for a RV, boat, toys etc. The shed with power can be used for additional storage or as a place to work on your DIY projects. The HOA provides snow removal, road maintenance and a private community boat ramp with access to the Deschutes River. Conveniently located close to Sunriver, Mt. Bachelor and the High Cascade Lakes.  Extra bonus: Short term rentals are allowed! This one won't last, make your showing appointment today.
